title: The GTA 6 Leaker Got Away With It...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the conclusion of what happened to the person who leaked over 50 videos of a leaked build of GTA 6 about a year ago. With this person getting away in the sense of not being fit for a trial just what comes next for one of the biggest mistakes I've seen in a while? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
